message.body: Thank Lynn and hunter for the brownies!!!
How are you doing? Is the house in Shirley ok?
I've been at lynn's. Won't be in shirley until tomorrow because we are not allowed in, but there is flooding!
I just found out that the water did not hurt the house. No large-scale flooding. The water came up to the 1st third of the driveway. No power as yet.
Aunt joesy lost her house in a placed called Breezy Point.
Ok that's good about Shirley. You told me about aunt joseys house, that sucks. Dibo also had a house in breezy point that burned down
